{"tid":1014420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★To支？】稅務學會前會長不主張派錢 應投放在社會最有迫切需要方面","createTime":"2019-02-09T07:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T09:27:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0b1d306815bdce4de4b012bc4505b3bd5323023d","tid":1014420,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T07:34:10.000Z","msg":"政府新一份財政預算案將於本月底公布，香港稅務學會前會長王銳強今早(9日)出席電台節目時表示，今個財政年度的賣地收入可能由上一個財政年度逾1600億港元，下調至不足1200億港元，但首三季盈餘仍有590億港元，相信整體盈餘能達500億港元。<br />\n<br />\n不過王不主張政府派錢，認為應該在社會最有迫切需要方面投放資源，以及投資未來，包括醫療、安老及房屋問題，以解決基本民生問題。<br />\n<br />\n會計師公會稅務師會執行委員會主席蘇國基就指，早前啟德土地拍賣流標，影響賣地收入，預計本年度的財政盈餘約為400億港元，與政府去年初預計相若。他亦稱，目前無出現超額盈餘，當局沒有太大壓力需要派錢，亦不樂見「無差別」派糖，擔心所謂的短期紓困措施常規化，會令社會有期望每年派糖，如果未來經濟出現逆轉，而政府工程開支增加，或會對整體盈餘帶來隱憂。他建議若政府有財政資源及能力可以減稅，並為中產提供租金稅務優惠。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190209/bkn-20190209091125521-0209_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190209%2Fbkn-20190209091125521-0209_00822_001.html&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jIwy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=baa2266f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190209/bkn-20190209091125521-0209_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f6d17e2ccc995c104aa6c9bcb1208a355926880d","tid":1014420,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T07:34:37.000Z","msg":"唔派=all in支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ebdd4bf1ed348759bcd1704aa7c4bfa8353791","tid":1014420,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T07:36:08.000Z","msg":"嗱 你唔好交表啊"},{"pid":"0d538b0da47d2c79e1b635a785d94dc1b892ba24","tid":1014420,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T08:07:25.000Z","msg":"政府每年攞八千萬去資助打golf，<br />\n又要起呢樣嗰樣好多使費㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每日150 香港要養呢班人唔窮都難啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1103b6787571801e336d66b0f58da608ba03761","tid":1014420,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T08:16:18.000Z","msg":"你唔主張派錢 但d錢比依個撚屌政府管理 特別係條波叔 屌那星派錢好過喇"},{"pid":"a09f1e33f12edf23bed504ef6ef572054eeab8b9","tid":1014420,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T08:23:37.000Z","msg":"大灣區要錢"},{"pid":"a7ef9eeda050c3f3fd2bdf80bfbc1d0ffa0eee4e","tid":1014420,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T08:52:51.000Z","msg":"而家個問題係唔派錢都唔會益到真香港人呀on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446d99f1f22806c329c69a0335601d7becf8354b","tid":1014420,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1103b6787571801e336d66b0f58da608ba03761","tid":1014420,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T08:16:18.000Z","msg":"你唔主張派錢 但d錢比依個撚屌政府管理 特別係條波叔 屌那星派錢好過喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:27:16.000Z","msg":"X2"}]}